Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.36,0:11:10.52,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反应弹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.61,0:11:13.22,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有这玩意儿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.29,0:11:23.66,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全体天顶星人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.12,0:11:27.34,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说这颗星球上沉睡着了不得的宝藏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.59,0:11:28.87,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有飞船和它
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.90,0:11:30.43,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们就自由了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.51,0:11:34.21,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小人们出现前
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.53,0:11:37.00,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙的支配者是我们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.42,0:11:39.39,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗 掠夺
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.56,0:11:42.06,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重现我们当年的荣光
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.35,0:11:49.94,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天顶星 天顶星
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.79,0:11:54.58,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.73,0:11:59.21,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你啊 计划还算顺利
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.65,0:12:01.52,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.56,0:12:33.52,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貌似反应弹的保管库被打开了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.80,0:12:50.60,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别上蹿下跳的 小人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.34,0:12:56.82,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SMS的机体被…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.90,0:12:59.72,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掩护 允许开火
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.89,0:13:03.67,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开干了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.26,0:13:05.06,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还击
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.07,0:13:11.64,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反应弹的搭载呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.64,0:13:12.42,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.87,0:13:14.39,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随时待命
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.29,0:13:17.98,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们一开始就这打算
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.65,0:13:20.10,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 小人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.63,0:13:22.27,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唱首歌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.67,0:13:25.63,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定能阻止我们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.78,0:13:41.04,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能再耽误了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.47,0:13:42.73,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发射舰炮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.12,0:13:52.37,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰桥听令 舰炮准备
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.50,0:13:55.53,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.75,0:14:03.51,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿鲁多 有你的生日礼物快递
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.04,0:14:12.14,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家 拥抱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.60,0:14:14.46,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到银河的尽头
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.20,0:14:29.39,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兰歌
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.28,0:14:50.99,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那女孩是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.25,0:14:52.99,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您不认识吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.73,0:14:56.53,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她就是把握代演机会
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.54,0:14:58.29,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,踏上巨星之路的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.88,0:15:01.83,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超时空灰姑娘！兰歌
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.82,0:15:06.99,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能 会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.94,0:15:11.27,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还以为肯定赶不上演唱会了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.39,0:15:57.39,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.36,0:16:11.27,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 混账
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.73,0:16:21.93,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿鲁多
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.31,0:16:33.94,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兰歌 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.83,0:16:45.53,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一群蠢货 被轻易驯服
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.62,0:16:56.33,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要除掉她
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.37,0:16:59.80,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休想
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.43,0:17:04.56,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死心吧 你败了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.69,0:17:05.66,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴 闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.93,0:17:07.92,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不许对我发号施令
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.52,0:17:16.57,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文化？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.65,0:17:17.48,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌声？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.56,0:17:19.72,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逗人笑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.97,0:17:22.53,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗才是我们天顶星人的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.85,0:17:24.76,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的血液
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.65,0:17:28.31,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继承着血液
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.94,0:17:31.27,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,近似于诅咒的演绎者之血
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.91,0:17:38.15,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们就是为此而被制造的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.53,0:17:41.16,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能以此为生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.38,0:17:50.43,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么演绎者之血
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.84,0:17:53.76,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不管呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.61,0:17:56.13,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.52,0:18:12.66,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我记住
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.35,0:18:15.31,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙再大
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.34,0:18:18.51,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也容不下两个种类的生物
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.44,0:18:37.73,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了不起啊 这姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.99,0:19:07.29,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疯了吗你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.32,0:19:10.65,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞行服都不穿 血肉之躯上战场来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.17,0:19:13.10,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不那样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.66,0:19:16.75,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家也许不会投入听…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.31,0:19:22.85,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知为什么 一放松腿就…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.15,0:19:26.19,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兰歌 你到底为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.33,0:19:29.60,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为想亲口传达
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.12,0:19:34.46,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生日快乐 阿鲁多
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.80,0:19:55.04,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.58,0:19:58.48,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想永远这样飞下去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.91,0:20:00.80,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.74,0:20:07.34,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,返程交给你了 阿鲁多
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.43,0:20:09.46,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘记了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.72,0:20:11.92,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兰歌的首演是明天
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.37,0:20:14.56,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要用上它
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.70,0:20:20.19,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别担心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.31,0:20:22.28,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢丽尔有我带回去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.53,0:20:23.57,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.31,0:20:28.76,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,体谅下兰歌冒险来这里的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.58,0:20:34.17,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…兰歌
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.22,0:20:36.26,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.86,0:20:39.13,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么好感谢的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.51,0:20:41.92,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我自己想来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.46,0:20:44.93,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过多亏你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.59,0:20:48.43,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是最棒的礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.66,0:21:12.91,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天空吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.32,0:21:28.98,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.71,0:21:30.81,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,操纵…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.41,0:21:44.50,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该死
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.21,0:21:56.00,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.75,0:22:07.46,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿鲁多 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.15,0:22:10.02,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.47,0:22:15.58,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.69,0:22:20.89,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Macross
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.46,0:23:55.67,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然出现的第一代Macross舰
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.06,0:23:58.08,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其雄姿再现时
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.23,0:24:00.85,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿鲁多见证了星球的命运
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.46,0:24:03.47,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 Memory of Global
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.75,0:24:06.01,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,激扬的歌声 响彻银河
